{"tid":1530460,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"個人認為港鐵會跌返去30蚊樓下","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T06:42:34.000Z","uid":32934,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c6acf7caa67a956939fe03a2bd6d4a8c234c9647","tid":1530460,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"以香港為發跡地既港鐵(前地鐵公司)背棄香港人，<br />\n與強權政府合謀，現今已失去民心。<br />\n交通收入對其業務實屬輕微，<br />\n但若引發更多破壞的行動，將引致經營成本上升。<br />\n若香港市民杯葛港鐵商場及站內商站，<br />\n或會引在一陣退租潮，大幅減低收入。<br />\n再者，若連登攬炒組如登報告誡歐，澳政府，<br />\n迫令港鐵撤出當地業務，那麽港鐵將嚴重重創，<br />\n介時港鐵股價或許會回復至30蚊或以下。"},{"pid":"458b03096f80dcbb10f68e056bb66db7fa5b6391","tid":1530460,"uid":226466,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:21:36.000Z","msg":"money doesnt pick sides in politics. so i disagree"},{"pid":"6b239ec1cf0e1a7953b07858cc24d1647f42530b","tid":1530460,"uid":161374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"地鐵有得加價，破壞車站影響唔大<br />\n<br />\n只有樓市大跌先會影響到佢核心利潤"},{"pid":"3bca91fbdc44f9db5e7db272c49179e8e7d1bfa9","tid":1530460,"uid":50347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:25:15.000Z","msg":"沽左先算"},{"pid":"8dff069493f052ffffa03610797090770782f263","tid":1530460,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"92684e88e6139db30925e4473db7074ad7f31e48","tid":1530460,"uid":296119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"樓跌佢先會跌<br />\n鐵路收入可以不理"},{"pid":"dc8c08a67277680a85ca8c9bca918ae98c3af083","tid":1530460,"uid":138713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:43:52.000Z","msg":"沽!"},{"pid":"85d58a1d9ee63bc081d95bf969d06d7750ee893c","tid":1530460,"uid":54177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"一開市又跌多4%， 姐係息都蝕埋，<br />\n沽佢老母+ put啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj